{"id":"a4c7b9ea51b74a1284bf4136c6e5d9ef83039acbaa6f94224ae4e2bfb089ebd8","item_id":"6934757cd6:0","text":"要向对象添加 user attribute（用户属性），可通过 Edit Parameter Interface（编辑参数界面）添加。"}
{"id":"12a0c0a38a81d17260e5e61ea567f7c6022cc17bb5c25e66d63ea704f87d6cea","item_id":"6934757cd6:1","text":"在 RenderMan 选项卡中的 Attributes 或 Primvars 区段下，将参数添加到 User 选项卡。该参数必须位于 User 文件夹内，并且必须带有 \"ri_user_\" 前缀才能被读取。"}
{"id":"9efc5c389d265dfcfbaf2630f1952757381cabc967f15e6fd768f2b57fc5950a","item_id":"6934757cd6:2","text":"还必须为该参数提供 Tag Value，用来告知 Houdini 和 RenderMan 该参数类型，并允许交互式编辑。"}
{"id":"53c732bab0242ef0ce1b3889f8087c1acec296f9dc78acc8ef3f7004b384202a","item_id":"6934757cd6:3","text":"以 MatteID 设置为示例"}
{"id":"cce01ce55b2ab50f0814b270b8126bebe42c2e4e2f0fa3f9e06809c077af7a34","item_id":"6934757cd6:4","text":"创建一个名为 \"ri_user_MatteID0\" 的 color attribute（颜色属性）。"}
{"id":"397f9e7e3d2609643926d4bb4606edb92c787a98cb0004f9a99ab895b6bd05dc","item_id":"6934757cd6:5","text":"label 是 UI 中显示的名称。"}
{"id":"e661a0a824eb9491690c86a3810e8ac16f6fb03e1377c8c57b7700ac8f1ac825","item_id":"6934757cd6:6","text":"注意，我们使用了靠近底部的 tags 字段，这是为了告知 Houdini 和 RenderMan 该 RenderMan attribute（RenderMan 属性）。有效值类型如下。"}
{"id":"059f5d260bf9dbb2ec2298e7c988771c2eb783a4b42a499f3676e58667494fe2","item_id":"6934757cd6:7","text":"有效的 Tag Values 列在这里。它们必须匹配左侧名为 \"Create Parameters\" 的窗格中所选 Parameter（参数）的预期数据类型："}
{"id":"6da88c34ba124c41f977db66a4fc5c1a951708d285c81bb0d47c3206f4c27ca8","item_id":"6934757cd6:8","text":"int"}
{"id":"76a7e234dc54e9c605b2cc9fdf71279526150df48c574bdfa69e436e0b3d5c18","item_id":"6934757cd6:9","text":"float"}
{"id":"74284d9dcbcc09928ca5d7d6187270a62ac1b58ccdc4a44b81e47257ffa53b9e","item_id":"6934757cd6:10","text":"color"}
{"id":"251fecd592e56e6c4a95121752f4a73bb802dffc1cc4bce6100206ee2b7cb650","item_id":"6934757cd6:11","text":"point"}
{"id":"b0d51c58c8b9c1f458fadf16c7d375630ef51da4df81915893b05c0fa4ed8bc6","item_id":"6934757cd6:12","text":"vector"}
{"id":"317b32c143692b9939c197f6a5df54f9698df9a4882fe8bf19608968662be4fa","item_id":"6934757cd6:13","text":"normal"}
{"id":"8674aab0dfc2483b62c5b5f10c167037acb4fcd9cea122db7913c747ac7d2efb","item_id":"6934757cd6:14","text":"hpoint"}
{"id":"6e00cd562cc2d88e238dfb81d9439de7ec843ee9d0c9879d549cb1436786f975","item_id":"6934757cd6:15","text":"matrix"}
{"id":"473287f8298dba7163a897908958f7c0eae733e25d2e027992ea2edc9bed2fa8","item_id":"6934757cd6:16","text":"string"}
{"id":"26ded777e9b5659ed9e120efa70a225b4b397e0d582705998c7fd0011b5c5203","item_id":"6934757cd6:17","text":"这会向 RIB 输出如下内容。"}
